{"title":"塞外之冬","authors":["王钧兵","峭岩"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":11,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外之冬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王钧兵画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峭岩诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个寒冷写成的传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫成树的圣洁，山的庄重"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原野里不再有夏的青翠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋的醉意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然有猎人的跋涉鹿的嘶鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，塞外之冬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——假如我离你千里万里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定会听到你的回声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似乎没有风雪的凛冽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有“白雪公主”的体态晶莹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里似乎没有荒漠的冷寂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却有母亲的豁达少女的温情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，塞外之冬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——假如我每晚都这样睡去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定会有一个甜甜的雪梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}